                        <div class="post post-simple post-sm">
                            <a class="post-img-link" href="about-us.html"><img src="images/image-17-310x200.jpg" alt="" width="310" height="200" /></a>
                            <h5 class="post-title"><a href="about-us.html">Intense is the most powerful Bootstrap theme</a></h5>
                            <div class="post-text">I’ve always cared about great visual design, but a few years ago I learned that I loved to teach as well. That led to starting this blog, building iPhone apps...</div><a class="btn btn-secondary post-btn" href="about-us.html">Read more</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="widget">
